@hongdjienoei  is a well-known art curator in Indonesia. Oei Hong Djien's passion for painting led him to devote his entire life to preserving Indonesian art.

He proved his loyality by opening a private OHD museum in Magelang, Central Java. The OHD Museum aspires the young generations to appreciate, enjoy and preserve Indonesian art. He will be our speaker at Ideafest and share about Indonesian art. Don't miss a chance to meet him and hear his stories.

