Firmansyah Mastup is the owner of Jakarta Vegan Guide, that aims to help vegans and other conscious people navigate Jakarta.

@fmastup graduated from a hotel high school in Jakarta and worked in several hotels with different positions. After he decided to turn vegan, he found very little media coverage on vegan places in Jakarta. That is when the concept of Jakarta Vegan Guide came.

